## üìã common configuration files

| file | purpose | validation tool |
|--------------|---------|-----------------|
| `package.json` | npm package configuration | `jsonlint` |
| `tsconfig.json` | typescript configuration | `tsc --noemit` |
| `webpack.config.js` | webpack build configuration | `webpack --validate` |
| `babel.config.js` | babel transpiler configuration | `babel --validate` |
| `.eslintrc.js` | eslint linter configuration | `eslint --validate-config` |
| `pom.xml` | maven project configuration | `mvn validate` |
| `build.gradle` | gradle build configuration | `gradle build` |

